ttps://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/PFk6J2z6lLlnHOKxd4mhehUCQslAY7c-eI-4XUQY2eCCHOw8gn4rjtYUoVS559sGaILIKvQjm-HYQtBEnL6HGnistQMWor9ZqoWg2jVyKvD7UAqStpBT-9EkY-XaFMubjamaOeXCrDRM8OZ7Wi-SNznrZ60Dc0PcUL-vWZsxnn9APNqAA_8WwKEfnodnga_fJROw-AJgPiFnrfltbim-lPCg4TfVj2-duxKXOfJ20mPAQiQHRDobgpgGbAv9rlzNeR7mzdxZvGsr4QkYv16Q9ISgjQ0D4CtjbngdkJplbqtjkhMBXDxTc8IlV__BU10r08voblC0et0cX1Tc5B_51lCD4gJ3ZlNTcYgFnhdMjFlQy0vZ_52pnhuENmQ/H6BXLSbL4DE_jTr8SHWwatrGlBUDPULr/7" target="_blank"&gt;生气”和“非常生气&lt;/a&gt;”。但是他后来告诉《空军一号》记者，他认为普京不会“ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/oU28H5DEhBqZLL-11iwq8NqQzmz5Eu1npnUu0G1ym98tCXh2AO3hCZwpyzMwW0YpALoD8jtaYwN-FfOH6vqjd4STY9EtjZnq-wy_2whet1qdoqKoopiNLX3iKvYvC-UF-9gX3IOmQLEtQWZNZnThETpeLgUJplaWIRwcPSX1posbGKJu1XH0ZrBkEX4GoP6AMYrytsw-5c6DZR-9mMKvxFFKM10cQicdDgnIbkn1mdPHk_FmbjcMvVGONUhELsPAPpXYCyHDvy32Cetn6iLUs0ooB0-CZjS1sYu5zHAo9UQiY3YwcD23G0ZELBXWby4G8wCArvypzcwMHq5rs_tBBw4y7RH4BFQI7Z-vR_BXggP_N2Csz2I13RWT7d8/trvfdGD2aqNmR9V0Yr8r_KVGiSHh6_XQ/7" target="_blank"&gt;回头说&lt;/a&gt;”，这似乎使一些埃奇奥夫（Edgeoff）受到了批评。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;埃隆·马斯克（Elon Musk）为X投资者带来了&lt;/strong&gt;意想不到的胜利，X投资者自从接管社交媒体平台以来一直经历了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/TObbJUWiu70l7eFC7qjoaysinNE0jx08qEjCsJgy1k5fdgMxIApt6utzRZK1lyYxmv1aGhXVEVqjqvdXZLpfJ61UoMUFzoB2C80lptmb-ItjqI_rQS15fSWGgI2PlDYJV22h-zcYqI82HHv53l6ckqJWEL4K5GFNtmpAdoBE8aD-qD5yUCB-Z0OvC9rb4ChjCzJBngSpgWF0D4sInt10QwFLpc9I7TkyEC4Ns0qZYXNo7d4CnJB6kHVMJF-F_gXDmnJvXuokBk3Y_mUduiEubCt9MfNqAZHktZja3Aj3Ky-S_lf44uQbXp4UsrFu7xYpigXgcTiqzS2uLhOGUmXHymvb7TGRM5YK-IHKCvNthGQQGQ-NIFbEHNffVWs/FHdzbq703R1s5kz4bOw0OR0uUToRu221/7" target="_blank"&gt;两年多的不确定性&lt;/a&gt;。他的人工智能创业公司Xai将以330亿美元的价格购买X，不包括债务。这意味着X Investors现在拥有新生AI初创公司的股票，具有&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/JB4GOS0yOeR3Ugye2mx-qWEYqsIVi9tyM-du_Xr41kUHzhzLouQv2H-HfpuSG-NiveJMNtvp3XeLVuos_Oh2e8p-hnTzyXfRnSv32enmZ1HIKeUva7-N0xRRaP