 style="padding-left: 10px; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;该计划符合首席执行官蒂姆·库克（Tim Cook）的更广泛的愿景&lt;/strong&gt;- 该公司将为&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/aEc66s3KVAbH5eEVtKDlR6yVz9BJPQpY1bfklSAGHFKWsmtVIThEE9UgggzGcQHsgh2Ju_ZsZVbYQyZ_gnj-3-cz03LhSq28wL3NxO2QOMMt8DAX3B7-zc55g3Hj9ODxY8P298PR3ZHAZZiPMEtcZ1c6ncHO-htMZ-7ICvc0ycsR9bwUyqwTIFQC5ja711Ch-phFU6UOxnXTcdAGDu2c9LNMg4VfvvlMoZYu6DDSD_SYZZPMCgsRiMXKY56RKgtgnynoIm5gnwqiFDKMy3HajI-cMNw0F-ShH8G8FSWam2ljiKB2oRgKAEh_QNgkjJ7WYm9v4GMqxBmf7eJQQpmcybi3J65s4GUAeu6RNQB7eGxFClY7ncFkpz2y4v8/up8MGNrpUnEXf-NMl5Tt-w4Ay4OmKDr1/7" target="_blank"&gt;医疗保健社会做出最大的贡献&lt;/a&gt;。例如，考虑其在期待已久的无葡萄糖监测仪上的工作。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;健康应用计划&lt;/strong&gt;于几年前首次出现。目前，这家技术巨头正在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/a7lV6ytB2txyiNdGnBsCGzZ7AgzfnWA3523EcQE5iV4OkehgTx3-XRk3d68f21zCzVpHxpMkh_hZpuYaUM3BooPIYkBTUkdSyT8pZpJvr8khmYc2s5yqBL5cfLh41gdyvuUNjKxyQwgKJR5PjesoMXdwwu2rrMIojxxbJKzqLpFfWkN3lY5IE5f3gEWGWuk7c7-U5b2cidPHU3tCaDqoB2jMIBHHyZf38n5C84TArFchZyUuDL5nl9R73X7nFPTw15kSrkYQGhquwLmjWIj94W70sI1_R55EBSUPBJUwccZvmjz6xB1U1KjRhja28YGMxkeZZma3gnfwdTT8WAnA9Vd5g0UMaPC9VD0nWeMlm7zI30H9jETL1N4eaKc/hBvKUY3OYp6GMxP2QzoxzSBEz4KEMIm7/7" target="_blank"&gt;培训代理商&lt;/a&gt;的员工医生数据。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;但是值得注意的是&lt;/strong&gt;，苹果一直&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/nOHtnVJr0H7m1Gm5jpbdxyGjkfZcJuU_5HerY_M5wbnpw7roX_p2xnYGzeeZ6MRhrh_-OQZsQ9tWV_SVBregE0aBPHugSd5GnkWS66ZM783piSYtubedbrgc3VTTsrClan3waT9np1UBecj0aMqrzh9cqlYad1Iq3didGJvtmCdswwo_1CL6uweG_-M3SFmc9GCARzrA6lOQgc-VoBDLz8IInilyZr0K34uFcBqJBe70n34hyzj2zkBp27KmAv_Rt-0SsCUtYsJ3vc3j0ndHnpaKQJaEWqYCMcXTPiBHHst9U86AFkUvu75vGtdrj2Ol5Sja2tiZ3HAJNXMqQ-bcrNROiUqTdiPuYK_3dwQJIhTK1FTr5YPZ90