Q7Xe-WTKSxnC5mMcMvh9qo6QW-oNFRPjnNdV61GisGflFCEEHRtiN-ChxliJ4UkQBoxDPVs9eL7mp_v9AytFkkmIpplT2EqPIwmowm8ITIiXA0q3f2GXfzFTDzh2NNgM7eXo7QVDcWtJdmz9z1hUr09eiN_9vdE-CZobfhV2yniU9VYpqXuc_j03TvIs67LuBkc5YnlnoGCD4k_9CuY0yziw7hr2jWMT8_KXfD1xsUsaiqflAexDj6noHxRlgvry8PZuKJaUi_7T4ZCFfbs2pgvgboiAJwAsSprR56HJGOn_SM-ozpZqHye5ZPip770HIGV3mIaJUlhLq2eJzR_JTF7iXyBIwiZvzjkGk/juZyYhZSA9-rn4J8EoRR543uNHpNZwts/7" target="_blank"&gt;加速涉及气候变化的反馈回路&lt;/a&gt;。温暖，更黑暗，更开放的海水吸收了太阳能，否则冰块会反映出冰。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;联合国认为欧洲在气候下可以做得更好。&lt;/strong&gt;联合国气候变化局的负责人西蒙·斯蒂尔（Simon Stiell） &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Vrt655KX1U8Lb5LF6DyLKw1bSass8L1wpswf-SzYuFBElE1W0QR_khx0n0WKY5eis21c8HNEZ6INygePIYLx9q5idKk2BcpnVPMRGkXitYq2GXrIJXsg6WBG_uWT357GhN1-jF0ZE5ZhdBexUwxJegwHxkIE9vhz1OlMuwN3ragR3xbUfUpcbCxMMe6orayEcpOdYAAqvidr3e-KpKsxAMMHI509fRjiKuO64li_zMjedjDkOZ1pXjA6vp3OFdTSvEC1HeGCjuteGTCuirdiFtrxTMG-szCrnUQ11Mpkf-8qdFrZZaP7NWr6N49NYH-zI9fd_XZ4SRCezFHtpBIntv4T6cChLvoSpGJtX82gHOxgLWRP5r7UlrK-iHg/DRRfHw_8JT8hvtN4hX2H8HcxfrjlMr8K/7" target="_blank"&gt;呼吁欧盟&lt;/a&gt;尚未向联合国提供最新的气候计划。他说：“您拥有技术，拥有资源；现在需要的是领导。”&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;气候谈话正在下降500指数&lt;/strong&gt;。平均而言，公司比三年前谈论的环境少76％。 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/QO6wfMWzEcSLf3wXUIATw5Vu3CTCtFFkD8o6qXmxf1QdRLL7aB6OToCaCT8PrFZ8u5h-dRHIT04w0DEiQv3dD8fihZLLP1tNNF7UmVxAKHKL_maP1jaL6g76HPsdkNR2X7WIq31O6y7NXXZpAC5-JSdTJ2PSEomRbWLAxHPXP6If-h2ne-D8vp0AHOHT5ESzLturzoH7sT5lKGuwOi5jbhf0Ck5FbFQUWirSyrPMwk9SxySoEi_SvmsS0_32RoKLOcrJC-KqNANVfmdZaxJWTh0kdAuNBMjK8RG5tsEsDgF_WSDl2pk4KrM7TUDt95V5t_kA4eAyJUeg93TwzqDV-V46okEyMzFE3WEJVNES5qfr-wTjBPLNx25-Jhw/g6wydraRu8Z4-94x5lF5XMwk2GqYMXog/7" target="_blank"&gt;绿色聊天最大的跌倒&lt;/a&gt;在于该指数的消费者酌处，财务和能源部门。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;根据伍德·麦肯齐（Wood Mackenzie）和美国清洁电力协会（American Clean Power Assocociation）的新数据，&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;美国的家用电池存储在2024年飙升了64％&lt;/strong&gt; 。现在，大约有50万户主的房屋拥有&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/RyjSx7o0Tye1a5HdOfNfYIKmXUD4dKwtczavKmfwHeUDOqZb4ku1sUNsUMcbR9wtlUCKf_CyJvL4hhg4H7g5-futYd-fytc33bjgd__G4bdzyHfd7NBTCtyddwxMtgniDgmpxFtja6y850B2Ltooxka9_W9ui7f7nDM0c10-M5r6RHegZUCSx6_q3iUFWQlGJkMcp2CExyeQU5i1DGTiF7_Kptphx7pLY2Y-Nh-5vWt_2OYxLVxLC7tTN4Cmxf5aRLTSd2C9hNLzl9TMFe2xSK21U-EUm5PMbNRZG8fIUPKJ6HLJpMOKWzjzAmAt82M2l9eC5aEaMZ1VzoRfejCiqoU0WZdF8yFLwbJZkVhEAqmP24jZP7U7hFrSpKk/8LogZGDGoXK0-Lc41hsr2Feu2SrTRYHs/7" target="_blank"&gt;3,028兆瓦小时&lt;/a&gt;的电力。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li style="font-family: Georgia, serif;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;只需停止油“挂高的景象”。&lt;/strong&gt;气候抗议组织表示，由于其最初要求终止未开发的石油和天然气领域许可证的要求，它将&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/ccdSCZAX_JUoHIwFg1uDoAfTOe-cF8zUeKb8TV5nDs52_77hmDUz77SHT8AmTKpr7CZRpvDfLSy5skgMQKOpAQDB3jhWBsDMmJeN21DL_npf-Uw7x49oVLlHwRDWZnjH0Eco1oB3nhmLDpI7EOoUiJ_bZ6Z9uNjWc6Jrmi3CuA0NldfBHEgjICHv8TRGk2gjfWlKekKuUCdObThAwa0qjbddS-S1F5eIjqUIwIdjpcb-mZgh5fA5Gbod50h6u-EXXFfkAIYSgYU9DUX0yvDZHJtqJmTPLyKftSYBPLRD5J5JNbtWUdMwhyd8e73G7pV-P_DxHRgGhV4xalgTKZ5kTMwjU5in_41kpHe6Q0IL1yzNjzoPKcnVH54db4I/N3djObh_SpptgFXYo7PvgTRNL4dkXzO5/7" target="_blank"&gt;不再进行颠覆性抗议活动，&lt;/a&gt;现在是英国的政府政策。该组织计划将于4月26日在伦敦议会广场举行最后一个“行动日”。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/dmx8wKc3lZWVcNwh3oAJKhCeOL8Ws5-LlIIsz1MEhTzY2cVUKTAPcVqOaW_JewDfTC5PIPtYxbT9DOZVVVng4Y9dcl-cHCfY3MGregvub7qbS2OzGFhxdTF_1iI_OfIWjg3ZSISekPrEtcsRh0BtcAgja-cGcgrp7pl1J1JEkZ1h9GblE-8-VDoaU4IyaBTeDZW5BrTi0UGBjAHJHNX2AG2BfoPD5Tl_qskmBbLyjGSKc2iNQKb2zfiyD-oUfRvMw3XDTsQYAcfUlWIHU2fjJXkadkW2XCMIZgSC7N1TKbNLHAy_fvsCnDifDIiwmYxZ_6QeXHMROGyH9hKSpytgLZQTesEeTG2ccQQHIdHugO5mhLg-aXPMsiPYKPc/eWFjq_DUlTJcxJZEY9DfPhV_46bAO2rc/7" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width